{
  "texts": [
    "In this study, we derived the embedding of the provided protein sequence from the ESM-1b transformer's output.",
    "This embedding was then integrated with EVCs and RCs to feed into PhiGnet.",
    "The integrated strategy offers insights into remote protein homology, leveraging informative relationships within the embedding representations of homologous proteins.",
    "This allows for generalization to previously unseen proteins in the training set.",
    "We encoded each protein sequence using a sequence-level embedding from the ESM-1b model."
  ]
}